==10月3日事故==
[[File:Pelagie_Islands_map.png|thumb]]之位置]]
2013年10月3日，[[義大利|義大利]]外海[[蘭佩杜薩島|蘭佩杜薩島]]附近發生一艘由[[非洲|非洲]][[利比亞|利比亞]]出發的[[難民|難民船]]翻覆事件<ref name=gp13>{{cite news|title=Scores of Migrants Dead After Boat Sinks Off Sicily|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/04/world/europe/scores-die-in-shipwreck-off-sicily.html?_r=0|accessdate=3 October 2013|newspaper=The New York Times|date=3 October 2013|first=Gaia|last=Pianigiani|location=Siracusa|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410010000/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/10/04/world/europe/scores-die-in-shipwreck-off-sicily.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>，總共造成359人死亡<ref>{{cite news |title=Mediterranean 'a cemetery' - Maltese PM Muscat |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24502279 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=2013年10月12日 |accessdate=2013年10月13日 |archive-date=2020年11月11日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111163051/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24502279 |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref><ref name=wdrb>{{cite news|title=Italian migrant death toll reaches at least 194|url=http://www.wdrb.com/story/23619837/italian-migrant-death-toll-reaches-at-least-194|accessdate=6 October 2013|work=WDRB.com|date=6 October 2013|first=Luca|last=Bruno|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014170757/http://www.wdrb.com/story/23619837/italian-migrant-death-toll-reaches-at-least-194|archivedate=2013年10月14日}}</ref>。義大利海岸巡防署已經救出155名生還者，此艘船相信載滿約500名乘客。<ref name=bbc>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24380247|title=Dozens of migrants die in Italy boat sinking near Lampedusa|work=BBC News|date=3 October 2013|accessdate=3 October 2013|archive-date=2013-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131003085046/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24380247|dead-url=no}}</ref>這些[[難民|難民]]多來自[[迦納|迦納]]、[[厄利垂亞|厄利垂亞]]以及[[索馬利亞|索馬利亞]]。<ref name=gp13/><ref name=bbc/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/10/04/witness-boat-migrants-used-bottles-to-stay-afloat/2922215/|title=Witness: Boat migrants used bottles to stay afloat|date=4 October 2013|publisher=USA Today|accessdate=4 October 2013|archive-date=2013-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205151146/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/10/04/witness-boat-migrants-used-bottles-to-stay-afloat/2922215/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===事故概要===
根據報導，這20[[公尺|公尺]]長的[[漁船|漁船]]載滿約500名的[[非洲|非洲]][[偷渡客|偷渡客]]，在距離[[蘭佩杜薩島|蘭佩杜薩島]]0.25[[海浬|海浬]]處發生引擎故障，因漁船嚴重超載導致船隻沉沒。<ref name=gp13/><ref name=bbc/>根據附近船隻上的目擊者說法，該難民船在故障之後發生[[火警|火警]]，許多偷渡客為避免火災紛紛跳入海中。但火勢隨著難民船所洩漏出的油汙延燒至海上，因此傷及許多跳入海中的難民。<ref name=bbc/><ref name=bbc2>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24392732|title=Italy sinking: Search resumes for missing migrants|work=BBC News|date=4 October 2013|accessdate=4 October 2013|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041448/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24392732|dead-url=no}}</ref>此次事故有約達200名的偷渡客[[失蹤|失蹤]]。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/oct/03/lampedusa-migrants-killed-boat-sinks-italy | work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | accessdate = 3 October 2013 | date = 3 October 2013 | title = Italy boat wreck: scores of migrants die as boat sinks off Lampedusa | first = Lizzy | last = Davies | archive-date = 2020-11-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128152506/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/oct/03/lampedusa-migrants-killed-boat-sinks-italy | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2013年10月4日，義大利海巡署共尋找到111具難民[[遺體|遺體]]，並救獲150名非洲偷渡客。該船隻之駕駛人為一於2013年4月遭到[[義大利|義大利]]強制驅逐出境的[[突尼西亞|突尼西亞]]籍35歲男子，在此次事件發生後該男子遭到義大利警方逮捕。<ref name=bbc2/>

==10月11日事故==
2013年10月11日，在10月3日[[地中海|地中海]]海域發生嚴重船難的後8天，距離上次發生船難的[[蘭佩杜薩島|蘭佩杜薩島]]120[[公里|公里]]處、[[馬爾他|馬爾他]]領海內發生難民船船難。此次事件共造成34名偷渡客死亡、50名偷渡客失蹤。根據報導，這些難民來自[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]以及[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]。[[義大利|義大利]]方面救獲的難民人數有56人，而[[馬爾他|馬爾他]]方面則是救獲134名偷渡難民。<ref name="BBC 24502279">{{cite web|title=Mediterranean 'a cemetery' - Maltese PM Muscat|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24502279|date=12 October 2013|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=12 October 2013|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111163051/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24502279|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbc 24499890">{{cite web|title='Dozens feared dead' off Lampedusa as migrant boat capsizes|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24499890|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=11 October 2013|archive-date=2013-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131011171402/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-24499890|dead-url=no}}</ref>

